sections.heading: Forester; personnel; employment
sections.text: In carrying out sections 85-162.01 to 85-162.05, the Board of Regents may employ such personnel to work under the State Forester as it shall deem necessary or advisable.SourceLaws 1967, c. 585, ยง 4, p. 1975;R.S.1943, (1981), ยง 85-163.05;Laws 1998, LB 922, ยง 412;Laws 2
